edu.uga.cs.recdawgs.entity

Interface User

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Administrator, Student

    public interface User
extends Persistable
    This is the base class of all registered users of the RecDawgs system. Each user has a first and last name, a user name (i.e., a login name), password, and an email address. The login name must be unique.
